name: fastcache
raw_meta_yaml:
schema_version: 1

context:
  name: fastcache
  version: 1.1.0

package:
  name: ${{ name|lower }}
  version: ${{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.org/packages/source/${{ name[0] }}/${{ name }}/${{ name }}-${{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 6de1b16e70335b7bde266707eb401a3aaec220fb66c5d13b02abf0eab8be782b

build:
  number: 8
  script: python -m pip install . --no-deps --no-build-isolation -vv

requirements:
  build:
    - if: build_platform != target_platform
      then: 
      - python
      - cross-python_${{ target_platform }}
    - ${{ compiler('c') }}
    - ${{ stdlib("c") }}
  host:
    - python
    - pip
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python

tests:
  - python:
      imports:
        - fastcache
        - fastcache._lrucache
      pip_check: true
  - requirements:
      run:
        - pytest
    script:
      - python -c "import fastcache; fastcache.test()"

about:
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: C implementation of Python 3 lru_cache
  homepage: https://github.com/pbrady/fastcache
  repository: https://github.com/pbrady/fastcache

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - synapticarbors
